PRIVACY POLICY
OVERVIEW
This privacy policy ("Privacy Policy") explains why information is collected and utilized by Faifly LLC and its subsidiaries and affiliated companies ("Faifly LLC", "our", or "we"). This Privacy Policy applies to Faifly LLC's website, https://memaster.faifly.com/ and also to Faifly LLC's apps including without limitations Memaster. We want you to know that we will handle all the personal information that will be identified below (Section 2) with the highest security standards and encryption. We encourage you to take the time to read this Privacy Policy to learn how we do so. Feel free to contact us if you require any further information. Also gather in mind that we might need to update this information from time to time. In that case you will be properly informed because, again, your acceptance will be required. NOTE: Your acceptance is essential to keep on playing and enjoying our products.
1. COLLECTION AND USE OF INFORMATION ABOUT YOU
Our main goal in collecting and using your private information is to improve your experience and new users' through our products. Information about you will be processed by us or through trusted third parties and it will be stored in the United States or in the EU through the best storage providers. The legal basis for the processing of your personal data is your acceptance and usage of our products. We cannot allow you to play our apps prior to your express consent of our Privacy Policy and Terms and Conditions.
2. COLLECTION AND USE OF INFORMATION ABOUT YOU
We collect the following personal information about you through the mentioned 3rd parties (section 1) or ourselves directly. Through your acceptance of this document and of our Terms and Conditions, you allow us and the trusted third parties to do the collection. We mainly collect the following data:
IP address
Gender
