Faifly LLC adheres to the Privacy Shield Principles for the collection and processing of personal data from our users in the European Union [and Switzerland]. To learn more about the Privacy Shield program please visit www.privacyshield.gov. Faifly LLC also adheres to the new Privacy terms described under GDPR https://www.eugdpr.org/ .
In compliance with the Privacy Shield Principles, Faifly LLC commits to resolve complaints about our collection or use of your personal information.
