Faifly LLC retains information about you for as long as necessary to fulfil the purposes for which we collected the data, except if required otherwise by law or yourself due to your right to withdraw your consent and to be forgotten. We may store information for longer periods for archiving or statistical purposes in which case we will take appropriate measures to ensure that the information is used solely for this purpose. Still, we do follow the right to be forgotten so we erase and encrypt data all the time and we will do it as soon as possible if you expressly require so.
9. COMPLAINTS
